4 HJR___ COMMENDING AND CONGRATULATING THE MCGILL-TOOLEN
5 CATHOLIC HIGH SCHOOL VOLLEYBALL TEAM FOR WINNING THE ALABAMA
6 HIGH SCHOOL ATHLETIC ASSOCIATION CLASS 7A STATE
7 CHAMPIONSHIP.
8
9 WHEREAS, highest congratulations are herein proudly
10 presented to the McGill-Toolen Catholic High School
11 Volleyball Team, located in Mobile, Alabama, for winning the
12 2025 Alabama High School Athletic Association (AHSAA) Class
13 7A State Volleyball Championship; and
14 WHEREAS, the team, known as the Dirty Dozen, defeated
15 Thompson High School 3-1 for its fourth straight Class 7A
16 Championship, making history as the first team to win four
17 in a row since the AHSAA adopted the seven-classification
18 format; and
19 WHEREAS, the victory over the Warriors (25-20, 29-31,
20 25-21, 25-17) is the program's 25th volleyball championship;
21 McGill-Toolen finished the 2025 season with an astounding
22 47-2 record; and
23 WHEREAS, among a roster filled with
24 championship-caliber athletes, several players delivered
25 exceptional performances: Class 7A Tournament MVP Catherine
26 McClain recorded 20 kills in the championship match; Bella
27 Smith led the team with 21 digs; Alice Wood totaled 17 digs
28 and four assists; Payton McClarren added 17 digs; and Cami
Page 1

and four assists; Payton McClarren added 17 digs; and Cami
